    <section class='html-notes'><h2 >Author Contributions</h2><div class='html-p'>Conceptualization, A.O. and E.A.; data collection, A.O.; analysis and interpretation of results, A.O., E.A. and W.S.; draft manuscript preparation, E.A. and W.S. All authors have read and agreed to the published version of the manuscript.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2>Funding</h2><div class='html-p'>The authors received no specific funding for this study.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Institutional Review Board Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>Not applicable.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Informed Consent Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>Not applicable.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Data Availability Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>The original contributions presented in the study are included in the article, further inquiries can be directed to the corresponding author.</div></section><section id='html-ack' class='html-ack'><h2 >Acknowledgments</h2><div class='html-p'>The authors sincerely acknowledge the Princess Sumaya University for Technology for supporting steps of this work.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Conflicts of Interest</h2><div class='html-p'>The author declares that there are no conflicts of interest to report regarding the present study.</div></section><section id='html-references_list'><h2>References</h2><ol class='html-xx'><li id='B1-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='1.'>Masood, I.; Daud, A.; Wang, Y.; Banjar, A.; Alharbey, R. A blockchain-based system for patient data privacy and security. <span class='html-italic'>Multimed. Tools Appl.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>83</span>, 60443–60467. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=A+blockchain-based+system+for+patient+data+privacy+and+security&author=Masood,+I.&author=Daud,+A.&author=Wang,+Y.&author=Banjar,+A.&author=Alharbey,+R.&publication_year=2024&journal=Multimed.+Tools+Appl.&volume=83&pages=60443%E2%80%9360467&doi=10.1007/s11042-023-17941-y" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11042-023-17941-y" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B2-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='2.'>Vats, T.; Kumar, S.; Singh, S.K.; Madan, U.; Preet, M.; Arya, V.; Bansal, R.; Almomani, A. Navigating the landscape: Safeguarding privacy and security in the era of ambient intelligence within healthcare settings. <span class='html-italic'>Cyber Secur. Appl.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>2</span>, 100046. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Navigating+the+landscape:+Safeguarding+privacy+and+security+in+the+era+of+ambient+intelligence+within+healthcare+settings&author=Vats,+T.&author=Kumar,+S.&author=Singh,+S.K.&author=Madan,+U.&author=Preet,+M.&author=Arya,+V.&author=Bansal,+R.&author=Almomani,+A.&publication_year=2024&journal=Cyber+Secur.+Appl.&volume=2&pages=100046&doi=10.1016/j.csa.2024.100046" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.csa.2024.100046" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B3-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='3.'>Ogundipe, D.O. The impact of big data on healthcare product development: A theoretical and analytical review. <span class='html-italic'>Int. Med. Sci. Res. J.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>4</span>, 341–360. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+impact+of+big+data+on+healthcare+product+development:+A+theoretical+and+analytical+review&author=Ogundipe,+D.O.&publication_year=2024&journal=Int.+Med.+Sci.+Res.+J.&volume=4&pages=341%E2%80%93360&doi=10.51594/imsrj.v4i3.932" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.51594/imsrj.v4i3.932" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B4-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='4.'>Ibeh, C.V.; Elufioye, O.A.; Olorunsogo, T.; Asuzu, O.F.; Nduubuisi, N.L.; Daraojimba, A.I. Data analytics in healthcare: A review of patient-centric approaches and healthcare delivery. <span class='html-italic'>World J. Adv. Res. Rev.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>21</span>, 1750–1760. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Data+analytics+in+healthcare:+A+review+of+patient-centric+approaches+and+healthcare+delivery&author=Ibeh,+C.V.&author=Elufioye,+O.A.&author=Olorunsogo,+T.&author=Asuzu,+O.F.&author=Nduubuisi,+N.L.&author=Daraojimba,+A.I.&publication_year=2024&journal=World+J.+Adv.+Res.+Rev.&volume=21&pages=1750%E2%80%931760&doi=10.30574/wjarr.2024.21.2.0246" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.30574/wjarr.2024.21.2.0246" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B5-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='5.'>Sharma, P.; Barua, S. From data breach to data shield: The crucial role of big data analytics in modern cybersecurity strategies. <span class='html-italic'>Int. J. Inf. Cybersecur.</span> <b>2023</b>, <span class='html-italic'>7</span>, 31–59. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=From+data+breach+to+data+shield:+The+crucial+role+of+big+data+analytics+in+modern+cybersecurity+strategies&author=Sharma,+P.&author=Barua,+S.&publication_year=2023&journal=Int.+J.+Inf.+Cybersecur.&volume=7&pages=31%E2%80%9359" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B6-applsci-14-10808' class='html-x' data-content='6.'>Pool, J.; Akhlaghpour, S.; Fatehi, F.; Burton-Jones, A. A systematic analysis of failures in protecting personal health data: A scoping review. <span class='html-italic'>Int. J