            <div class="additional-content">
                <h2><a name="cite"></a>Share and Cite</h2>

                <div class="social-media-links" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Privacy-Preserving%20Data%20Sharing%20in%20Telehealth%20Services&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3053448%3A%0A%0APrivacy-Preserving%20Data%20Sharing%20in%20Telehealth%20Services%0A%0AAbstract%3A%20In%20today%26rsquo%3Bs%20healthcare%20industry%2C%20safeguarding%20patient%20data%20is%20critical%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20digitization%20of%20medical%20records%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20cyber%20threats.%20Telehealth%20services%2C%20while%20providing%20immense%20benefits%20in%20terms%20of%20accessibility%20and%20efficiency%2C%20introduce%20complex%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20data%20privacy%20and%20security.%20This%20paper%20proposes%20a%20privacy-preserving%20framework%20for%20secure%20data%20sharing%20within%20telehealth%20services%2C%20employing%20blockchain%20technology%20and%20advanced%20cryptographic%20techniques.%20The%20framework%20ensures%20that%20all%20patient%20health%20data%20are%20encrypted%20using%20homomorphic%20encryption%20before%20storage%20on%20the%20blockchain%2C%20guaranteeing%20confidentiality%20and%20protecting%20data%20from%20unauthorized%20access.%20Secure%20multi-party%20computation%20%28SMPC%29%20is%20integrated%20for%20encrypted%20data%20computations%2C%20maintaining%20data%20confidentiality%20even%20during%20operations.%20Smart%20contracts%20enforce%20access%20control%2C%20ensuring%20that%20patient%20preferences%20and%20regulatory%20requirements%20such%20as%20the%20HIPAA%20and%20the%20GDPR%20are%20met.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20framework%20includes%20auditing%20and%20verifying%20data%20integrity%20mechanisms%2C%20making%20it%20resilient%20against%20cyber%20threats%20such%20as%20impersonation%2C%20replay%2C%20and%20Man-In-The-Middle%20attacks.%20The%20analysis%20demonstrates%20the%20framework%26rsquo%3Bs%20superior%20performance%20in%20addressing%20these%20challenges%20compared%20to%20that%20of%20existing%20systems.%20Future[...]" title="Email">
